      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 49.4</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 49.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>信者，吾信之；不信者，吾亦信之，德信。聖人在天下歙歙，為天下渾其心，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The sage has in the world an appearance of indecision, and keeps his mind in a state of indifference to all.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
